comment:
* Columns that appear when each row of a table belongs to a specific
     * account, including sync information that an account may need.
     *
     * @see RawContacts
     * @see Groups

variables.name: ACCOUNT_NAME
variables.comment:
* The name of the account instance to which this row belongs, which when paired with * {@link #ACCOUNT_TYPE} identifies a specific account. *

Type: TEXT

variables.name: ACCOUNT_TYPE
variables.comment:
* The type of account to which this row belongs, which when paired with * {@link #ACCOUNT_NAME} identifies a specific account. *

Type: TEXT

variables.name: SOURCE_ID
variables.comment:
* String that uniquely identifies this row to its source account. *

Type: TEXT

variables.name: VERSION
variables.comment:
* Version number that is updated whenever this row or its related data * changes. *

Type: INTEGER

variables.name: DIRTY
variables.comment:
* Flag indicating that {@link #VERSION} has changed, and this row needs * to be synchronized by its owning account. *

Type: INTEGER (boolean)
